<div class="home-container">
  <div class="row intro-home-row full-width">
    <div class="small-12 small-centered home-column columns">
      <h1>Welcome to Tyto</h1>
      <a href="#" class="button radius">Teacher Demo</a>
      <a href="#" class="button radius">Student Demo</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row teacher-home-row full-width">
    <div class="small-12 small-centered columns home-column">
      <div class="small-12 large-5 columns">
        <h3>Teachers:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Assign work to students</li>
          <li>Monitor individual proficiency levels for subjects</li>
          <li>Automatically text selected parents when assignments are created</li>
          <li>Filter class roster by struggling students</li>
          <li>Send messages to classes in a chat window</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="small-12 large-7 columns">
        screenshot
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row student-home-row full-width">
    <div class="small-12 small-centered columns home-column">
      <div class="small-12 large-7 columns">
        screenshot
      </div>
      <div class="small-12 large-5 columns">
        <h3>Student dashboard:</h3>
        <p>Students can view a list of their assignments and invitations to classes. They also have access to a chat box for each class they are in so they can discuss problems with teachers and classmates.<p>
        <h3>Student assignments:</h3>
        <p>Students complete problems in a problem set. Problems increase in difficulty as the student's measured proficiency increases. The assignment is complete when the proficiency score reaches a certain level or when the assigned number of questions are completed. Students can also watch a video on the assignment topic and notify their teacher when a problem is difficult.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row parent-home-row full-width">
    <div class="small-12 small-centered columns home-column">
      <div class="small-12 large-6 columns">
      <h3>Parents:</h3>
      <p>Parents can choose to receive texts when their children get new assignments.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="small-12 large-6 columns">
        <%= image_tag('iphone.png') %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
